{"tid":1652540,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[賽後檢討] 記住要FACT CHECK! 唔好再去錯地方裝修喇","createTime":"2019-10-13T17:11:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T17:44:18.000Z","uid":6630,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4eaaa904bac671aeda7577ab516339e847f8a8c1","tid":1652540,"uid":6630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:11:27.000Z","msg":"下午有網民發起在各區示威，其中在鰂魚涌柯達大廈二期，有人打碎大廈的玻璃門，噴上「大公可恥」的字樣，並向大廈掟汽油彈，消防和警員到場處理。<br />\n <br />\n翻查資料， 《大公報》過去曾有辦公室在柯達大廈二期，但目前已搬走。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/2525825204169751/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fphotos%2Fa.720050934747196%2F2525825204169751%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=0ZNtUZ9Qk1f13jNJdsSeN5mCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=b76e08cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/2525825204169751/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n睇返大公報個網寫嘅總部地址：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aZvxUCE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaZvxUCE.png&h=5cedaa2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.takungpao.com/corp/connect.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.takungpao.com%2Fcorp%2Fconnect.html&d=0ZNtUZ9Qk1f13jNJdsSeN5mCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=2d480e49\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.takungpao.com/corp/connect.html</a><br />\n<br />\n咁到底邊度仲係寫大公報總部喺柯達大廈呢，我又搵咗一搵：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mbDWBQx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmbDWBQx.jpg&h=e205681a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先，我哋唔係狗，出咗錯就要有承擔。既然波及無辜，最起碼都要晒個冧，建議和理非可以喺情況許可下去現場貼返啲道歉嘅notice。當然，喺我哋眼中，可能第一時間都會諗係咪鬼做，但係喺有實質證據之前，做一做形象工程都唔係一件壞事。<br />\n <br />\n另外就係最最最緊要嘅，「維基百科」同「香港網絡大典」唔係可靠嘅資料來源。喺度提一提大家點樣去check資料嘅真確性：<br />\n1. 返過大學嘅人都知，citation係唔可以寫維基百科，因為入面嘅資料係可以錯。上門裝修呢啲冇招牌又唔係舖頭嘅office之前，更加要fact check清楚先。<br />\n2. 最好搵返官方資料或者一啲權威性嘅網站，例如公司網。<br />\n3. 同時盡可能搵超過一個source以便cross check，防止好似今次咁信錯一啲outdated嘅資料。<br />\n<br />\nReference: <a href=\"https://africacheck.org/how-to-fact-check/tips-and-advice/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fafricacheck.org%2Fhow-to-fact-check%2Ftips-and-advice%2F&d=0ZNtUZ9Qk1f13jNJdsSeN5mCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=48ae67b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://africacheck.org/how-to-fact-check/tips-and-advice/</a>"},{"pid":"11f2622b61a02f461b6daf3e019a76eeab19ff76","tid":1652540,"uid":6630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:12:37.000Z","msg":"記住要FACT CHECK!"},{"pid":"1f32a94d30d17e0eacff74ee3035d18ee64a10d0","tid":1652540,"uid":6630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:13:19.000Z","msg":"記住要FACT CHECK!"},{"pid":"6bc4c72b86223b4b0436a60acfdb6448e42c0d17","tid":1652540,"uid":6630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:13:58.000Z","msg":"記住要FACT CHECK!"},{"pid":"80a97df42bec78ba02de6c4c5fa164e1a80680cb","tid":1652540,"uid":6630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:14:44.000Z","msg":"記住要FACT CHECK!"},{"pid":"141ed8eb82199c8777202fb7f53fbb30c6bc6217","tid":1652540,"uid":6630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:15:31.000Z","msg":"記住要FACT CHECK!"},{"pid":"cae66b765c6a71aeefdc1d6e301219d1785304ed","tid":1652540,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:15:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0725970e9b4504355b8003afced92e53bb1d1a60","tid":1652540,"uid":6630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:16:07.000Z","msg":"記住要FACT CHECK!"},{"pid":"f887de8054a956c7638c9ade8b94948337110a32","tid":1652540,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:16:42.000Z","msg":"檢討先有進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"429bd2f6a8a32e248061a10d1260